/' -------------- Innlogging ------------- '/
User -> Frontend: Log inn with \nusername + password
Frontend -> Backend: Username +\n password
Backend -> Database: Username +\n password
Database -> Backend: OK
Backend -> Frontend: OK
Frontend -> User: Now signed in

